Package: tsmarch
Type: Package
Title: Multivariate ARCH Models
Description: Feasible large scale multivariate Autoregressive Conditional Heteroscedasticity (ARCH) models including Dynamic Conditional Correlation (DCC), Scalar BEKK (Indirect DCC), Copula GARCH and Generalized Orthogonal GARCH with Generalized Hyperbolic distribution. A review of some of these models can be found in Boudt, Galanos, Payseur and Zivot (2019) <doi:10.1016/bs.host.2019.01.001>.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alexios", "Galanos", role = c("aut", "cre","cph"), email = "alexios@4dscape.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-9308-0457")))
Maintainer: Alexios Galanos <alexios@4dscape.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), methods, tsmethods (>= 1.0.2)
